@startuml TransactionLogger

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam classFontStyle bold
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam nodesep 50
skinparam ranksep 30

title Diagram Kelas TransactionLogger & LogEntry

class TransactionLogger {
    - entries : vector<LogEntry>
    __
    + TransactionLogger()
    + log(turn : int, username : string, actionType : string, detail : string) : void
    + getFullLog() : const vector<LogEntry>&
    + getRecentLog(n : int) : vector<LogEntry>
    + getEntryCount() : int
    + clear() : void
    + loadEntries(entries : vector<LogEntry>) : void
}

class LogEntry {
    + turn : int
    + username : string
    + actionType : string
    + detail : string
    __
    + LogEntry(turn : int, username : string, actionType : string, detail : string)
    + toString() : string
}

' Relasi
TransactionLogger *-- "0..*" LogEntry : stores >

note right of TransactionLogger
    <b>Mencatat seluruh kejadian signifikan:</b>
    DADU, BELI, SEWA, PAJAK, GADAI,
    TEBUS, BANGUN, LELANG, FESTIVAL,
    KARTU, BANGKRUT, SAVE, LOAD

    <b>Digunakan oleh:</b>
    - GameEngine: memanggil log() setiap aksi
    - SaveLoadManager: serialize/deserialize log
    - CommandProcessor: CETAK_LOG → getRecentLog()
    - GUI: renderLog() untuk menampilkan
end note

note bottom of LogEntry
    Data class sederhana.
    Satu entri = satu kejadian dalam permainan.
    Contoh:
    turn=5, username="Uname1",
    actionType="BELI",
    detail="Beli Jakarta (JKT) seharga M400"
end note

@enduml
